            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#00aa00' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>                 Declining trend</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#f5f5f5' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#f5f5f5' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>= inventory accumulating faster than dispatch</run>
